  "name": "The Chief Clerk's Visit",
  "description": "The chief clerk arrives at the Samsa apartment to investigate why Gregor has not reported for work. The family pleads through the locked door while Gregor struggles to operate the lock with his mandibles. When he finally opens the door, the clerk retreats in horror and flees the building. Father forces Gregor back into his room with a walking stick. This is the moment the transformation becomes a collective family crisis rather than Gregor's private problem.",
